response.overview: Tracks Through Time, narrated by Dennis Weaver, tells the story of the Denver & Rio Grande Railroad's motivation to build the line in 1881 and captures the history through the years. Enjoy the beauty of the trip on board the historic Durango & Silverton Narrow Gauge Railroad as the train winds through the San Juan Mountains of Southwest Colorado.
response.tagline: A living history of the Durango & Silverton Narrow Gauge Railroad & Museum
response.title: Tracks Through Time
